{"word":"διικνέομαι","slug":"διικνέομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διικνέομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ίξομαι</el>) (aor2 <el>-ικόμην</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to go through, penetrate</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>:— <i>to reach</i>, with missiles, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>in speaking, <i>to go through, recount</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}